    <p>{`Click on the `}<strong parentName="p">{`escalation policy`}</strong>{` you want to remove the schedule from, then click `}<strong parentName="p">{`Edit Escalation Policy`}</strong>{` on the top right corner of the page.`}</p>
    <p><img parentName="p" {...{
        "src": "https://files.readme.io/620058e-editing-schedules-edit-ep.png",
        "alt": null
