    <p>{`Find your `}<strong parentName="p">{`schedule`}</strong>{` in the `}<strong parentName="p">{`Notify the following users or schedules`}</strong>{` field, then click the `}<strong parentName="p">{`X button`}</strong>{` on the schedule object to remove it from the rule.`}</p>
