          }}></path></svg></a>{`Restore a Schedule to a Previous Version`}</h2>
    <p>{`If you or another user alters a schedule in an undesired way, you can quickly revert a schedule back to a previously saved version. This feature also allows you to see when each saved change was made.`}</p>
    <p>{`To revert a schedule:`}</p>
    <ol>
      <li parentName="ol">{`Click on `}<strong parentName="li">{`Configuration ➡️ Schedules`}</strong>{`.`}</li>
      <li parentName="ol">{`Click on the name of the schedule that you wish to revert to open its details.`}</li>
      <li parentName="ol">{`On the right hand side of the page, click on `}<strong parentName="li">{`Revert this Schedule`}</strong>{` to view the recent changes made to that schedule.`}</li>
    </ol>
    <p><img parentName="p" {...{
