      <li parentName="ol">{`Once you select one of the options from the dropdown, you will be brought to the Edit Schedule page for that version of the schedule. From here you may make additional edits, or click on `}<strong parentName="li">{`Revert Schedule`}</strong>{` in the upper right corner of the page.`}</li>
